product_name: Tissot Couturier Chronograph Black Leather Men's Watch
description: A quality quartz movement is the substance behind the outer style of this Tissot Couturier collection. Featuring hours, minutes and a small second counter, the dauphine hands call to mind the designer’s scissors. In addition to the stopwatch function is a date display. This is an action-packed piece in an understated, 41 mm case. 10 bar (100m/330ft) water resistance and sapphire crystal are additional practical features of this watch with classic good looks. For fashion aficionados and those with discerning tastes the choice of quality leather straps or metal bracelet is one that will make all the difference to the final look. T035.617.16.051.00

product_name: Tissot Chemin Des Tourelles Powermatic 80 42 mm Green Men's Watch
description: The Tissot Chemin des Tourelles is a showpiece of Tissot’s expertise in traditional watchmaking and a key collection in our Classic selection. The watch named after the street in Le Locle where Tissot is located in the heart of Swiss watchmaking country has become a firm favourite with watch lovers over the years. This new range demonstrates refinement at every turn – from design to functionality and everything in between. A range of case sizes, finishes and variety of dial and strap colours ensures that this most classic of watches can also be personalised to suit modern tastes. T139.407.11.091.00

These modern yet classic timepieces provide sophistication and an enduring design suitable for everyday wear in both casual and formal situations. With an array of options, there is a model to suit everyone. T129.410.16.013.00

product_name: Tissot Seastar 1000 Powermatic 80 Black Men's Watch
description: Readable, reliable, robust: The Tissot Seastar 1000 merges style and performance without compromising either. With water resistance of up to 30 bar (300 m/1000 ft), screw-down crown and case back, it is our ultimate sports watch. The screw-down crown also offers additional protection against knocks. This latest model harnesses the energy of the awesome Powermatic 80 movement with its impressive extended power reserve. This is a high-quality Swiss-made watch you can rely on to keep you safe.
